{"tid":918197,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"貝澳Billy逝世 膠袋塞滿胃","createTime":"2018-11-27T04:30:12.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-27T04:46:32.000Z","uid":102732,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"a886888146bbfceda8daeec82d5884e7646f3dc3","tid":918197,"uid":102732,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-27T04:30:12.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E8%B2%9D%E6%BE%B3billy%E9%80%9D%E4%B8%96-%E8%86%A0%E8%A2%8B%E5%A1%9E%E6%BB%BF%E8%83%83-224530482.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.yahoo.com%2F%25E8%25B2%259D%25E6%25BE%25B3billy%25E9%2580%259D%25E4%25B8%2596-%25E8%2586%25A0%25E8%25A2%258B%25E5%25A1%259E%25E6%25BB%25BF%25E8%2583%2583-224530482.html&d=kPlvPdLcVkc%2Fw3cbopP%2FZgKEmdudW1rq3V1Y15kzxIU%3D&h=53771b66\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E8%B2%9D%E6%BE%B3billy%E9%80%9D%E4%B8%96-%E8%86%A0%E8%A2%8B%E5%A1%9E%E6%BB%BF%E8%83%83-224530482.html</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/DdPQtq96A.y9vWrRND9gNg--~A/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9NjAwO2g9NDUwO2lsPXBsYW5l/http://media.zenfs.com/en_us/News/skypost/20181127JAD001__20181127_L.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2FDdPQtq96A.y9vWrRND9gNg--~A%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9NjAwO2g9NDUwO2lsPXBsYW5l%2Fhttp%3A%2F%2Fmedia.zenfs.com%2Fen_us%2FNews%2Fskypost%2F20181127JAD001__20181127_L.jpg&h=39b08cb1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n【晴報專訊】大嶼山貝澳唯一一隻小黃牛Billy近日去世，有關注本港牛隻人士於網站發文哀悼，認為遊客不當餵飼及居民胡亂棄置垃圾等，均是Billy死因之一。漁護署在Billy的腹部發現大量膠袋，數量足以裝滿兩個垃圾桶，呼籲市民切勿餵飼流浪牛。<br />\n<br />\n漁護署昨於其facebook專頁宣布Billy的死訊，指Billy平時會自行在貝澳一帶草地覓食，直至近年有遊客開始餵Billy食人類食物，改變其覓食習慣，Billy就不時走入沙灘、營地向遊客「搵食」，還不時「摷開」膠袋，誤以為有膠袋便有食物。署方指，檢驗後發現Billy整個胃都是膠袋，導致腸道阻塞，而這些膠袋足以裝滿兩個垃圾桶。<br />\n<br />\n被餵飼改覓食習性<br />\n<br />\n署方呼籲市民勿餵飼流浪牛，因牠們擁有於野外自行覓食的習性，有些牛隻習慣被人類餵飼後，會主動向遊客搶食物，甚至在垃圾箱覓食，包括膠袋。而牛隻進食人類餵飼的食物後，或因突然改變食物種類及進食模式，導致消化不良、阻塞食道；或因消化系統出現過敏反應，導致不適及消瘦等。<br />\n<br />\n由關注本港牛隻市民設立的社交網站facebook專頁「梅窩牛牛都哪裏去了？」日前亦發文透露Billy已逝世，指牠愛亂吃垃圾，近年其健康狀況持續變差，毛色暗啞、腹部腫脹，卻骨瘦如柴。<br />\n<br />\n大嶼山愛護水牛協會主席何來指，現時大嶼山約有200隻黃牛，梅窩及昂坪亦是牛隻亂吃垃圾的重災區，呼籲遊客不要餵飼及親近牛隻，應尊重當地環境。<br />\n<br />\n周圍掉垃圾正仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ecf04ae255347ab97f662f48eddf481c2451ded6","tid":918197,"uid":71508,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-27T04:33:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6aeff8e0c9f0a30975ea5bfd6542f3f2e6549da4","tid":918197,"uid":85659,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-11-27T04:34:42.000Z","msg":"丟垃圾都唔係問題<br />\n<br />\n餵牛真係ON撚9<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1a1fdb3ff369c0194d4cb5d4ef7d820a5fcdd450","tid":918197,"uid":141871,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-27T04:38:38.000Z","msg":"好掛住佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n露營冇得見佢喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"17c1d669a1a828dacfaa2b17a704da8551466aa3","tid":918197,"uid":6752,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6aeff8e0c9f0a30975ea5bfd6542f3f2e6549da4","tid":918197,"uid":85659,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-11-27T04:34:42.000Z","msg":"丟垃圾都唔係問題<br />\n<br />\n餵牛真係ON撚9<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-27T04:41:49.000Z","msg":"大撚把人餵白鴿,馬嬲仲理直氣壯添啦"},{"pid":"640ee59ba83daab2d92470e9c90f0c4a1f52ca1d","tid":918197,"uid":198245,"like